00:04:06.610 --> 00:04:08.530
Finally, we will look at the stocks.

00:04:08.970 --> 00:04:10.090
I will explain how it works.

00:04:10.970 --> 00:04:12.970
The change in stock at the

00:04:12.970 --> 00:04:14.890
