00:04:14.890 --> 00:04:15.650
result.

00:04:15.750 --> 00:04:17.170
We consider it an income.

00:04:17.410 --> 00:04:19.870
However, it should be noted that it has not

00:04:19.870 --> 00:04:21.670
resulted in an increase in the amount of money.

00:04:21.830 --> 00:04:23.450
We must adjust it in the same way.

00:04:23.450 --> 00:04:27.090
We have an income that has not increased

00:04:27.090 --> 00:04:28.310
the balance of the cash.

00:04:28.410 --> 00:04:29.650
This increased the balance of another

00:04:29.650 --> 00:04:31.070
